item.title: tarUnarchiver for Google Apps Script
item.description: Overview This is a script for extracting files from a tar file using Google Apps Script. This script was created by native Google Apps Script. The following 3 situations gave me the motivarion for creating this script. Although I had been looking for the script for extracting files from a tar file from before, I have still not been able to find it. Unfortunately, there are no methods for extracting the files from the tar file in Google Apps Script.
